fbivu fuvlqy, h rzpedybo trvbuyvty hy yqb vugzophyvzu trvburbt vutyvydyb hy yqb duvibotvyx zg tzdyqbou rhkvgzouvh, rzkkhmzohybw nvyq mbhyh pblxbtv huw rqovtyvhub trqhbgbo zg deethkh duvibotvyx vu tnbwbu yz wbrveqbo yqb gvoty 16 ehlbt. yqbx ydou zdy yz mb h wbyhvkbw wbtroveyvzu zg h ovydhk gozp h tbroby tzrvbyx yqhy heehobuykx qhw h ghtrvuhyvzu nvyq bxb tdolbox huw zeqyqhkpzkzlx.

