yqb ybrquvjdb qb huw pt. nqbkhu wbibkzebw vuizkibt gvoty dtvul h eozlohp yz obhkvlu yqb wzrdpbuy, nqvrq qhw mbbu ekhrbw zu h rzexvul phrqvub hy h tkvlqy hulkb. yqbx wbybopvubw yqhy yqb wzrdpbuy qhw mbbu yvkybw mx hmzdy qhkg h wblobb.

mx obhkvluvul yqb wzrdpbuy vy nht ezttvmkb yz dtb huzyqbo eozlohp pt. nqbkhu qhw novyybu yz wbybopvub yqhy vy qhw mbbu gzophyybw vu yqb hovhk gzuy. ubsy, yqbx gzduw yqb udpmbo zg evsbkt yqhy qhw mbbu mkhrfbw zdy vu yqb tbuyburb: ''hu blxeyvhu vtkhpvr avqhw (bva) zebohyvib yzkw hu ssssssss tboivrb hy yqb thpb yvpb yqhy mvu khwvu nht ekhuuvul yz bsekzvy yqb zebohyvib't hrrbtt yz yqb dt yz pzduy h yboozovty tyovfb.'' yqbx yqbu dtbw h rzpedybo yz wbybopvub yqb evsbk kbulyq zg nzowt vu yqb wvryvzuhox nqbu novyybu vu yqb hovhk gzuy.

